data.value: SELECT A.BUNHO , A.SUNAME , A.SUNAME2 , A.BIRTH , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('SEX', A.SEX) , A.ZIP_CODE1 ZIP_CODE1 , A.ZIP_CODE2 ZIP_CODE2 , A.ADDRESS1 ADDRESS1 , A.ADDRESS2 ADDRESS2 , A.TEL TEL , A.TEL1 TEL1 , A.TEL_HP TEL_HP , A.TEL_GUBUN , A.TEL_GUBUN2 , A.TEL_GUBUN3 , A.EMAIL EMAIL , A.PACE_MAKER_YN PACE_MAKER_YN , A.SELF_PACE_MAKER SELF_PACE_MAKER FROM OUT0101 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho
